---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Reveal from '../../components/Reveal.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Company Setup in Florida – Aprire LLC e Corporation | [NOME BRAND]"
  description="Servizio amministrativo per aprire una LLC o Corporation in Florida. Coordiniamo il filing con il partner USA. Tempi e costi chiari.">

  <section class="pt-20 pb-12 md:pt-28 mesh-accent">
    <div class="container-x">
      <nav class="text-[13px] text-muted mb-8">
        <a href="/" class="link-underline">Home</a> <span class="mx-2">/</span> <span>Company Setup</span>
      </nav>

      <Reveal>
        <span class="eyebrow">Servizio amministrativo</span>
        <h1 class="display mt-7 max-w-4xl">
          Company Setup in <em>Florida</em>.<br/>Dalla scrivania italiana.
        </h1>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal delay={150} class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-soft text-[19px] leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Ti aiutiamo nella parte amministrativa per costituire una <strong style="color: rgb(var(--ink-900));">LLC</strong>
          o una <strong style="color: rgb(var(--ink-900));">Corporation</strong> in Florida.
          Coordiniamo tutta la procedura con il nostro partner statunitense, in italiano, con tempi e costi chiari.
        </p>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal delay={250} class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/company-setup-florida/pacchetti/" class="btn btn-primary px-6 py-3">Vedi pacchetti e prezzi</a>
        <a href="/contatti/" class="btn btn-outline px-6 py-3">Richiedi informazioni</a>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container-x grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-12">
      <Reveal>
        <span class="chapter-num">— Inclusi</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl mt-4">Cosa include il servizio</h2>
        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          {[
            'Verifica preliminare di dati e documenti',
            'Coordinamento del filing presso la Florida Division of Corporations',
            'Servizio di registered agent in Florida tramite partner',
            'Consegna digitale di Articles of Organization / Incorporation, EIN (se incluso)',
            'Supporto operativo in italiano durante tutto il processo',
          ].map((it) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--line));">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" style="color: rgb(var(--accent)); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px;"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              <span class="text-[16px] leading-snug">{it}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal delay={150}>
        <span class="chapter-num">— Esclusi</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl mt-4">Cosa NON è incluso</h2>
        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          {[
            'Consulenza legale, fiscale o contabile (italiana o USA)',
            'Valutazione personalizzata della forma societaria',
            'Dichiarazioni fiscali, contabilità, payroll',
            'Apertura conti bancari (dipende dall\'istituto)',
            'Tasse statali, fees governative e costi di terzi',
          ].map((it) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--line));">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" style="color: rgb(var(--ink-400)); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
              <span class="text-[16px] leading-snug text-soft">{it}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24" style="background: rgb(var(--surface));">
    <div class="container-x">
      <Reveal class="max-w-xl mb-16">
        <span class="eyebrow">Scegli la forma</span>
        <h2 class="display-sm mt-6">Due forme societarie diffuse in Florida.</h2>
      </Reveal>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <Reveal>
          <a href="/company-setup-florida/llc/" class="group block rounded-3xl p-10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
            style="background: rgb(var(--bg)); border: 1px solid rgb(var(--line));">
            <span class="tag tag-dot">Più diffusa</span>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl mt-6">LLC in Florida</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-soft leading-relaxed">
              Struttura snella e flessibile. Soci denominati <em>members</em>. Documento istitutivo: Articles of Organization.
            </p>
            <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium" style="color: rgb(var(--ink-900));">
              Scopri di più
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        </Reveal>
        <Reveal delay={150}>
          <a href="/company-setup-florida/corporation/" class="group block rounded-3xl p-10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
            style="background: rgb(var(--bg)); border: 1px solid rgb(var(--line));">
            <span class="tag">Strutturata</span>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl mt-6">Corporation in Florida</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-soft leading-relaxed">
              Struttura più articolata. Soci denominati <em>shareholders</em>. Documento istitutivo: Articles of Incorporation.
            </p>
            <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium" style="color: rgb(var(--ink-900));">
              Scopri di più
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        </Reveal>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container-x text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <Reveal>
        <h2 class="display-sm">Pronto a partire?</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-soft text-[17px]">Compila il form: ti contattiamo per un primo briefing in italiano.</p>
        <a href="/contatti/" class="btn btn-primary mt-8 px-6 py-3.5">Richiedi informazioni</a>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
